Curvy Brides showcases the plus-size bridal salon Curvaceous Couture, located
in Maryland. Owned and operated by sisters Yukia and Yuneisia, Curvy Brides
demonstrates that theres a dream dress out there for every woman, no matter her
size. Yukia herself struggled to find a designer wedding gown to suit her
curves, and that struggle inspired her to help other women get outfitted for
their special day. The sisters started out running a business in their fathers
basement, and now theyre running a boutique with gowns for plus-size women with
every taste and style. (Source: TLC)
